Admin Specialist (Contract under 3rd party)
Responsibilities
Under general supervision, works within a specialized function with work verified on an as needed basis.Reads and interprets documents such as safety rules, operating and maintenance instructions, procedure manuals, and service orders.Writes routine reports and correspondence.Requires ability to speak effectively with groups of customers or employees of organization. Will be dealing with Operations & Workshop personnel and supervisor on daily basis.Requires ability to perform basic numerical, statistical, and/or financial analysis.Applies common sense understanding to carry out detailed but uninvolved written or oral instructions.Maintain Record control of all documentations completed in each operation facilities. Compiling and verifying archival of documents.Support admin for Information Distribution and other task in relation to Quality ManagementSystem implementation Requirements : Skills are typically acquired through completion of Diploma Degree. Fresh graduates will be considered.Good command of oral and written EnglishDetails oriented3 position available : Jakarta, Balikpapan & Duri Only candidates who meet the qualifications and experience are invited to apply. Please send detailed resumes and application letters only. No other documents are required at this point.
